subject: College Athletics
Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament
lead_paragraph: Tina Charles had 29 points, 18 rebounds and 4 blocks to lead No. 1 Connecticut to a 77-63 victory over Penn State in the Maggie Dixon Classic at Madison Square Garden.
